<D>__{it's strong stuff.}
<A>__{jacob stretches out on the bed. he stares up at the ceiling and examines its pock marked lunar look. long cracks and shallow craters erode the surface. it is an alien terrain.}
<C>__{jacob}
<D>__{i think i'm falling asleep.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{pleasant dreams.}
<A>__{the words send a jolt through jacob's body. he tries to get up but can't. he's frightened.}
