<A>__{the ceiling begins to rumble. cracks split wide open. huge crevasses tear through the plaster. jacob's world is crumbling. he stares in horror as demonic forms attempt to surge through the rupture above him. piercing eyes and sharp teeth glimmer in the darkness. hooved feet and pointed claws clamor to break through.}
<C>__{jacob}
<P>__{(continuing)}
<D>__{help me!}
<A>__{instantly michael appears standing over him. he is holding the vial with the antidote. he draws an eyedropper full of the fluid and holds it over jacob's mouth.}
